<p>No. All scores from a test date will be reported together. &nbsp;&nbsp;<=
/p>
<h3>Can I Combine My Writing Scores From One Test Date With My Multiple-Cho=
ice Scores From Another?</h3>
<p>Yes - superscoring enables you to combine writing scores from one test d=
ate with multiple-choice scores from another test date.<br>
